From 48584c209c0f1b514ed89d1747cafe958870e9cd Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: grok-build-providers-verify <verify@invalid>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 16:56:01 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 11/14] Add dynamically controllable raw sampling logs

Record fully shaped raw provider request bodies alongside response SSE chunks. Use one process-wide gate initialized by GROK_LOG_SAMPLING/--log-sampling, keep the tracing layer dynamically interested, and expose hidden /debug sampling on|off|status ACP controls with a full-payload privacy warning.
